<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第83屆 講道會 第2講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/34">陳耀鵬牧師</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83">第83屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83#session-master-42">講道會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第二講  虛懷若谷、心感不足				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="799"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-end align-items-center"><div>
				</div></div>				<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">曾有文章說明「八福」與香港人的觀念的差異，內容大意如下：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">「八福」談虛心，但香港人卻求勝逞強。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「八福」談哀慟，但香港人卻不惜代價去尋樂，甚少為人為己哀痛。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.6pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">「八福」談溫柔，但香港人卻凡事為己爭取利</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">益，不甘心讓人佔便宜。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.6pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">「八福」談飢渴慕義，但香港人卻渴望優質生</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">活，心靈空間越來越小。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「八福」談憐恤，但香港人卻各家自掃門前雪，對弱勢者諸多批評</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「八福」談清心，但香港人卻營營役役求名利，心靈被蒙蔽，看不見神。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「八福」談使人和睦，但香港人卻凡事自求個人</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.2pt">利益。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:21.25pt; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「八福」談為義受逼迫，但香港人卻明哲保身，不追求公義。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;Adobe 繁黑體 Std B&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:normal"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">神與心靈痛悔謙卑的人同居</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.55pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">文章對香港人標籤化，過於負面。「八福」確</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">是跟社會的觀念不同。按世俗觀念言，有地位、有權</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">勢，才愈有福氣。八福也跟世俗宗教觀不同，可有</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">什麼宗教會教人以貧窮開始、以受逼迫為結束呢？聖</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">經所論的公義不是追求歡樂，聖潔也不是心理學所論</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">的自我實現或身心安康。不要以個人感受去改變那不變、絕對的真理，也不要以自己舒服的感覺來代替艱辛倫理的抉擇。當世人以投資有法、自給自足的人為有福，我們理當儆醒，持守八福真理，肯定天國子民</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.2pt">的品格。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.6pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">一封電郵提及各類物件的特質，提醒我追求天國子民的品格。它說花瓶外表漂亮，但內心空虛；瀑布居高臨下，卻口若懸河；汽球被人一吹，就飄飄然。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">相反合桃沒華麗外表，卻頭腦充實；指南針思想穩</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">定，東西南北都不被吸引。而給人最大提醒的是蝦，當牠大紅之日，正是大悲之時。若我們覺得自己有點成就時，切勿不可一世，自以為是，否則便是大悲之</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.3pt">時。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:1.25pt">「虛心的人有福了，因為天國是他們的。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.85pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">「虛心」應翻作「靈裡貧窮」，英語譯作</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">&rdquo;<span style="letter-spacing:.85pt">poor </span><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">in </span><span style="letter-spacing:.8pt">spirit</span>&rdquo;。「靈裡貧窮」不是指人垂氣喪氣，也不是<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">失去了鬥心、妄自菲薄，看輕自己，毫無主見，任人</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">踐踏，沒有理想動力方向；也不是指膽怯缺乏勇氣。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.85pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「靈裡貧窮」亦不是靈裡低落。靈裡低落的人從不領受神的恩典，忘記自己的身份，魔鬼就因它驕傲失去了自己的地位，而成了魔鬼。當我們作深刻反省時，沒有什麼值得我們驕傲，我們乏善足陳。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「靈裡貧窮」亦不是指物質貧窮。聖經並沒有以物質貧窮就是好事，否則基督徒也無需扶貧救災。教</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">會歷史對「貧窮」有兩種見解，一是指物質缺乏，另</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">一則是精神上自視貧窮，無論貧富，心裡捨棄了物質財富，為神願捨一切。但「靈裡貧窮」不是要求捨棄財富往深山修道。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">主關心的是靈裡的事，關乎人對自己的態度。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「靈裡貧窮」不是指靈裡低落，垂頭喪氣。「八福」所用的字眼解作赤貧、一無所有，如乞丐般，沒有資財，再無依靠，全然依靠上帝，如詩篇所言：「我這</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">困苦人呼求，耶和華便垂聽，救我脫離一切患難。」</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">（詩三十四</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">6）若綜合希臘文及希伯來文的意思，</span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">靈<span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">裡貧窮有福了，就是指靈裡自覺極端貧乏、一無所</span><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">有，完全需要依靠上帝的人有福了</span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">，「因為那至高至</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">上、永遠長存名為聖者的如此說：我住在至高至聖的所在，也與心靈痛悔謙卑的人同居；要使謙卑人的靈甦醒，也使痛悔人的心甦醒」（賽五十七</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">15）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;Adobe 繁黑體 Std B&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:normal"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">虛心</span></span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt"> -- 得神悅納的必要條件</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">被神所重用、被神呼召的基甸、摩西、大衞都</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">深感自己不配。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神呼召基甸從膽怯的農夫成為大能勇士，他說他家在瑪拿西支派中是至貧窮的，摩西也覺</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">得他不能承擔艱鉅責任，但因著他們謙卑順服神，最</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">終成就大事。<strong>每次我們得勝，都因著我們能虛心信靠</strong></span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.3pt">神。</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">彼得本是敢作敢為、充滿自信的人，但他遇見主時，深感自己的污穢，求主離開他；保羅有才幹，但</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">遇見了主，把一切看作有損。他以使徒身份寫第一封書信</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.05pt">--加拉太書，後寫信給哥林多教會，稱自己是使</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">徒中最小的，不配稱為使徒（林前十五</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">9）。他說自己比眾聖徒中最小的還小（弗三8）。甚至在臨終時</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">對提摩太說：「我在罪人中是罪魁。」他年紀越老，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">跟隨耶穌愈久，越看到基督的要求，看到耶穌的完</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">美，看到自己的虧欠不足。基督標準很高，我們理當</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">虛心。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">香港中文大學校長沈祖堯被稱為「沙士英雄」，也被亞洲週刊評為「亞洲英雄」。他覺得並沒有在沙士期間獲得勝利，在最無助時，最感到神的幫助，因此不覺得自己凱旋而歸，並表示這是他信主三十年以來與神最接近的時刻。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">虛心的人沒有驕傲自豪，深知離開了神，人不</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">能作什麼，人無所依靠，才幹家勢、國家都不足以自誇。英國某文學家說，莎士比亞進來時，我們都要站起來，耶穌進來時，我們就要跪下來。祂是獨一的救</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">主。一位著名丹麥雕刻家花了多年心血刻成耶穌雕</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">像，他的耶穌像低著頭，伸出手來，令人看不清祂的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">樣貌。一次一位高傲的著名學者參觀此像，他說：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">「這像有什麼希奇呢？連耶穌的樣貌都看不到！」旁邊有小孩子跑到他跟前說：「先生，你要走到此像前跪下來才能看見耶穌的樣貌！」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">謙卑跟虛心有什麼不同呢？只有謙卑的人才會虛心，虛心的人必會謙卑，當人看見自己的領受都從神</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">而來，原沒有可誇的，真正謙卑的人少講自己，也不</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">誇口。聖經裡講論羊的次數許多，羊甚是軟弱，及不上狗聰明，沒有獅子大膽，但神叫卑微的羊升高。求神幫助我們將內心的自我、驕傲降服於十字架下。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;Adobe 繁黑體 Std B&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:normal"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">深明自己污穢，但求神的憐恤</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.6pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">今年</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">6</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">月，冰上曲棍球北美聯賽冠軍戰，溫哥華</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">加人隊跟波士頓棕熊隊對壘，最後一場在溫哥華舉</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">行，加人隊落敗。賽後暴動，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">150</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">人受傷，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">15</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">部車輛</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">被毀，無數商店被搶，雖是少數人行徑，但有人反問我溫哥華不是很太平</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">?</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.05pt">&nbsp; 叫我無言以對，求神幫助我們</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">不可有虛榮，常學虛心捨己。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">「靈裡貧窮」的人應是一無所求，一無所知，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">一無所有。無求，指在神前完全不帶自我的企圖，只願實踐神的旨意；一無所知，即不知神在自己身上的作為</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">&nbsp; --</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">&nbsp; 不知神用上什麼方式、什麼時間來運行祂的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">旨意，不求神在他身上作為的解釋</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.2pt">(</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">那是恩典裡的奧</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">秘</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">)，只關注神在他身上作為的影響，只將自己交託</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.2pt">神。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.2pt">&nbsp; 一無所有，即認定世上並無任何屬於自己的，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">房子、生命全都不屬於自己，只是獲准享用，一切視為神所賜所交托，不能擁有。總括而言，「虛心」就是深明自己心靈污穢罪惡，乏善可陳，對自己能提升</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">靈命完全失望，單單祈求神的憐恤。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">為什麼八福以虛心為起始呢？要得蒙後頭的恩</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">典，虛心就是基礎。若不以虛心作起始，似是沒有根</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">的果子，人不覺靈性貧乏，豈會為罪哀慟？虛心對信</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">徒而言有三方面重要性：一、虛心是讓人得神悅納的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">必要條件，二、虛心是讓我們得救贖的必要條件，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">三、虛心也是屬靈成長的必要條件。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">虛心是讓人得神悅納的必要條件。大衞是虛心</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">的，他跟掃羅說自己出身卑微，豈敢作掃羅的女婿？他跟耶和華也是如此說，「主耶和華啊，我是誰？我的家算什麼？你竟使我到這地步呢？」（撒下七</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">18）馬利亞向天使說：「我心尊主為大，我靈以神我的救</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">主為樂，因為他顧念他使女的卑微</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">&hellip;&hellip;」耶穌降生</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">時，天使沒有向尊貴人顯現，只向牧羊人宣告，牧羊人身份卑微，連出庭作證的資格也沒有。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">西面、亞拿只是普通人，但專心等候以色列安</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">慰者，到聖殿來見耶穌，高舉神的名字。故此聖經有</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">言：「耶和華靠近傷心的人，拯救靈性痛悔的人。」</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">（詩三十四</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">18）登山寶訓似乎是座高山，靠自己無法爬上，要依靠神去爬，以虛心為起始，知道自己的弱點、無知，懷著虛心，坦然面對心裡的貧乏。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-right:.9pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;Adobe 繁黑體 Std B&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-weight:normal"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">不斷的虛心，不斷的成長</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">虛心乃是我們得救贖的必要條件，人若不虛心，無人能認識耶穌基督，唯有人到了盡頭，倒空自己，才能得著屬靈福氣。在佈道會裡，人舉手決志，決志禱告，為主作見證，這一切必先有先決條件，那就是</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">承認自己靈性破產，是個罪人，才能進到神的國去，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">「你們得救是本乎恩，也因著信；這並不是出於自</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">己，乃是神所賜的，也不是出於行為，免得有人自</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">誇。」（弗二</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">8-9）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">自我膨脹的人無法容得下基督，手拿石頭，又豈能再拿黃金呢？</span></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">水杯倒空才能盛滿飲料，虛心才覺得</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">耶穌寶貴，除非自覺有屬靈的需要，否則基督無法叫</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">我們滿足。人若不餓，怎會吃東西呢？生命的糧只會叫那些自覺靈裡貧乏的人得著滿足，除非虛心，否則不會覺得天國珍貴。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.9pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">虛心也是屬靈成長的必要條件，耶穌強烈指責老<span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">底嘉教會：「你說：我是富足，已經發了財，一樣都不缺；卻不知道你是那困苦、可憐、貧窮、瞎眼、赤身的。我勸你向我買火煉的金子，叫你富足；又買白衣穿上，叫你赤身的羞恥不露出來；又買眼藥擦你的</span><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">眼睛，使你能看見。」（啟三</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">17-18）人自以為靈裡</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">富足，卻是貧窮，人若沒有不斷的虛心，亦不能不斷成長。因此虛心是基礎，若要繼續得著屬靈的祝福，需要在這根基上繼續踏上，虛心總不會過時，願信徒</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">如靈裡的乞丐，時常在神的跟前承認自己靈裡破產。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">有一位神學生今年畢業，他花了八年完成本來 </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">3、4年的課程，期間5年以病人身份選讀神學。他有</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">三位朋友，第一位朋友是「沙士」，第二位朋友是骨</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">枯，第三位朋友是癌症。他是護士，在</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">2003年照顧</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">病人時，感染「沙士」，引致骨枯，後來患癌，仍堅</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">定事奉，他最喜歡教會團契的名字</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">--「耶執羔」，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">「執」是指檢拾回來，那是說耶穌檢拾來的羔羊。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:20.5pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">愛心、虛心、信心</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.05pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">有電視節目叫「感動香港」，介紹十位令人感動的人物：大排檔老闆為長者提供免費粥品、女士為無親無故的長者辦理身後事、生意人賣掉房子，將八成家產捐給教育事業、為民抱打不平的議員、走遍大江南北收集中草葯的教授、坐輪椅的女士，還幫助其他傷健人士、醫生到災區助人動矯型手術、幫助癌症病人身心康服的男士、一對建立私立大學的夫婦、窮婆婆節衣縮食幫助更窮的人。當中至少三位是基督徒，其中兩位公開感謝神。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:0cm; margin-right:21.2pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-left:0cm; margin:0cm 0cm 0cm 20.35pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">求神助我們透過八福品格的表現，告訴別人我們是光是鹽，並以虛心來作起始。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
				
				<br>
				<p class="h5">
					<span>講員：</span> 陳耀鵬牧師
				</p>			</div>
			<div class="article-navigation d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
